<section id="salesOrderSimple">
  <title><indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>sales orders</primary>
      <secondary>creating new simple</secondary>
    </indexterm>New Simple Sales Order</title>
  <para></para>
  <para>To create a new simple Sales Order, select the "New Simple" option.
  The following screen will appear:</para>
  <para><screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/salesOrderSimple.png" />
        </imageobject>
        <caption>Create New Simple Sales Order</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot></para>
  <para>When creating a new simple Sales Order, you are presented with the
  following options:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Order #</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Cust. PO #</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Customer</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Ship To</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Item Number</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Qty</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
  <para>The following buttons are unique to this screen:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>HOLD ORDER</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Select to </para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>NEW ORDER</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
  <para>To process payment for the Order, select the "Payment" tab. The
  following screen will appear:</para>
  <screenshot>
    <mediaobject>
      <imageobject>
        <imagedata fileref="images/salesOrderSimpleCCPay.png" />
      </imageobject>
      <caption>Credit Card Payment</caption>
    </mediaobject>
  </screenshot>
  <para>When processing a Credit Card payment for the Order, you are presented
  with the following options:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Credit Card</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Amount</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>CVV Code</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
  <para>The following buttons are unique to this screen:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>NEW</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>VIEW</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>CHARGE CC AND COMPLETE ORDER</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
  <para>To process a cash payment for the Order, select the "Cash" tab. The
  following screen will appear:</para>
  <para><screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/salesOrderSimpleCashPay.png" />
        </imageobject>
        <caption>Cash Payment</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot>When processing a cash payment for the Order, you are
  presented with the following options:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Order Total</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Balance</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Available Credit</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Amount Received</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Funds Type</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
        <variablelist>
          <varlistentry>
            <term>On Account</term>
            <listitem>
              <para></para>
            </listitem>
          </varlistentry>
        </variablelist>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Payment/Document #</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Payment/Document Date</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Post To</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
  <para>The following button is unique to this screen:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>POST PAYMENT AND COMPLETE ORDER</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
</section>
